<div
  class="container mx-auto p-10 bg-white dark:bg-dark-bg transition-colors duration-300"
>
  <h1
    class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-6"
  >
    Privacy Policy
  </h1>

  <div
    class="bg-white dark:bg-dark-surface shadow-lg dark:shadow-2xl rounded-lg p-8 border dark:border-dark-border transition-colors duration-300"
  >
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-primary leading-relaxed">
      Welcome to <strong>EventX</strong>. Your privacy is important to us, and
      this Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your
      personal information.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      1. Information We Collect
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2"
    >
      <li>Personal details such as name, email, and contact information.</li>
      <li>Account-related information, including roles and permissions.</li>
      <li>Usage data, including website interactions and log activities.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      2. How We Use Your Information
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2"
    >
      <li>To provide and manage user roles and access permissions.</li>
      <li>To improve user experience and website functionality.</li>
      <li>
        To communicate updates, security alerts, or service-related
        notifications.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      3. Data Protection
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2">
      We prioritize the security of your data and implement strong measures to
      prevent unauthorized access, data loss, or breaches.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      4. Third-Party Sharing
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2">
      We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties, except when
      required by law or to enhance security.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      5. Cookies & Tracking
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2">
      Our website may use cookies to enhance user experience and collect
      analytical data. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser
      settings.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      6. Changes to This Policy
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2">
      We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be
      communicated on this page.
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-dark-text-primary mt-6"
    >
      7. Contact Us
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-dark-text-secondary mt-2">
      If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
      <strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-dark-text-primary"
        >nitrreventportal@gmail.com</strong
